{"version": 2, "width": 90, "height": 35, "timestamp": 1774364951, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}}
[0.003432, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[0.004093, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;37m\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   🛡️  MCP Shield                                          ║\r\n  ║   One-command security for MCP servers                    ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   Powered by agentgateway (Linux Foundation)              ║\r\n  ║   github.com/bcornish1797/mcp-shield                     ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.004731, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m  THE PROBLEM: Most MCP deployments have ZERO security\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[6.005551, "o", "  A typical MCP client configuration (works with any MCP-compatible IDE):\r\n\r\n"]
[7.007964, "o", "  {\r\n    \"mcpServers\": {\r\n      \"filesystem\": {\r\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n        \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"/tmp\"]\r\n      },\r\n      \"memory\": {\r\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n        \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-memory\"]\r\n      },\r\n      \"github\": {\r\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n        \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"],\r\n        \"env\": {\r\n          \"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\": \"ghp_xxxxx\"\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n"]
[11.009482, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;31m  ⚠️  No authentication. No rate limiting. No audit logging.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[14.010725, "o", "\u001b[1;33m  THE SOLUTION: MCP Shield + agentgateway\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[16.011845, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 1: Score your security posture\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js score -f demo/sample-config.json\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.057123, "o", "\r\n🛡️  MCP Shield — Security Score Assessment\r\n\r\n"]
[18.057348, "o", "  Scanning 3 MCP server(s) from claude-desktop...\r\n\r\n"]
[18.057481, "o", "  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n  │                                                     │\r\n  │   \u001b[1;35mMCP Security Score:  F  (10/100)\u001b[0m                    │\r\n  │                                                     │\r\n"]
[18.057516, "o", "  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n"]
[18.057697, "o", "  ❌ Issues Found:\r\n\r\n     🔴 Authentication (critical)\r\n        No authentication layer between clients and MCP servers\r\n        → Run `mcp-shield secure --auth strict` to add JWT authentication via agentgateway\r\n\r\n     🟠 Rate Limiting (high)\r\n        No rate limiting — servers vulnerable to resource exhaustion\r\n        → Run `mcp-shield secure --rate-limit 60` to add token bucket rate limiting\r\n\r\n     🟠 Audit Logging (high)\r\n        No request/response logging — tool calls are invisible"]
[18.057712, "o", "\r\n        → Run `mcp-shield secure` to enable gateway-level audit logging\r\n\r\n     🟡 Endpoint Federation (medium)\r\n"]
[18.057872, "o", "        3 servers exposed as separate endpoints — increases attack surface\r\n        → Run `mcp-shield secure` to federate behind a single gateway endpoint\r\n\r\n     🟡 Input Validation (medium)\r\n        No schema-based validation of tool arguments at gateway level\r\n        → Deploy agentgateway with request validation policies\r\n\r\n     🟡 CORS Policy (medium)\r\n        No CORS headers configured — cross-origin requests uncontrolled\r\n        → Run `mcp-shield secure` to configure appropriate CORS headers\r\n\r\n     🟢 OAuth Discovery (low)\r\n        No .well-known/oauth-protected-resource endpoint for client auto-discovery\r\n        → Run `mcp-shield secure` to expose OAuth resource metadata\r\n\r\n     🟡 Server Isolation (medium)\r\n        All servers share the same access policy — no per-server RBAC\r\n        → Use `mcp-shield secure` to generate per-server endpoints with independent policies\r\n\r\n  ✅ Passed:\r\n\r\n     ✅ Transport Security\r\n"]
[18.058073, "o", "        All servers use stdio transport (local only)\r\n\r\n  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n  Servers scanned: 3\r\n  Checks passed: 1/9\r\n  Critical issues: 1\r\n  High issues: 2\r\n\r\n  💡 Run 'mcp-shield secure' to address all issues and improve your score.\r\n     After securing, run 'mcp-shield score' again to verify improvement.\r\n\r\n"]
[21.063234, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 2: Scan your existing MCP setup\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js scan -f demo/sample-config.json\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[23.101275, "o", "\r\n🔍 Scanning for MCP server configurations...\r\n\r\n"]
[23.101493, "o", "  📁 Source:  claude-desktop\r\n  📄 File:    demo/sample-config.json\r\n  🔧 Servers: 3 found\r\n\r\n  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n  │ MCP Servers                                            │\r\n  ├────────────────────┬──────────┬────────────────────────┤\r\n"]
[23.101517, "o", "  │ Name               │ Type     │ Command/URL            │\r\n  ├────────────────────┼──────────┼────────────────────────┤\r\n"]
[23.101655, "o", "  │ filesystem         │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n  │ memory             │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n"]
[23.101674, "o", "  │ github             │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n  └────────────────────┴──────────┴────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n  ⚠️  Security Assessment:\r\n    • Authentication:  NONE — any client can connect\r\n    • Rate Limiting:   NONE — no protection against abuse\r\n    • Audit Logging:   NONE — no visibility into tool usage\r\n    • Input Validation: NONE — tool arguments pass unchecked\r\n\r\n  💡 Run 'mcp-shield secure' to generate a secured configuration.\r\n\r\n"]
[26.106135, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 3: Generate secured configuration\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js secure -f demo/sample-config.json --rate-limit 60\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[28.142721, "o", "\r\n🛡️  MCP Shield — Generating secured configuration...\r\n\r\n"]
[28.143054, "o", "  📁 Found 3 MCP server(s) from claude-desktop\r\n\r\n  🔐 Generating JWT keypair for authentication...\r\n"]
[28.144977, "o", "     Public key:  mcp-shield-output/keys/pub-key\r\n     Private key: mcp-shield-output/keys/priv-key.pem\r\n\r\n"]
[28.150841, "o", "  ✅ Secured configuration generated!\r\n\r\n  📂 Output files:\r\n     mcp-shield-output/gateway-config.yaml  — agentgateway configuration\r\n     mcp-shield-output/claude_desktop_config.json  — client config (points to gateway)\r\n     mcp-shield-output/keys/  — JWT keypair\r\n\r\n  🚀 To start the secured gateway:\r\n\r\n     agentgateway -f mcp-shield-output/gateway-config.yaml\r\n\r\n"]
[28.150992, "o", "  Then update your IDE to use the gateway endpoint:\r\n"]
[28.151042, "o", "     http://localhost:3000/mcp\r\n\r\n  🛡️  Security features enabled:\r\n     • Authentication:  STRICT\r\n     • Rate Limiting:   60 req/min\r\n     • CORS:            configured\r\n     • Audit Logging:   enabled\r\n     • Federation:      3 servers → 1 endpoint\r\n\r\n"]
[31.15528, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 4: Start the secured gateway\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ mcp-shield start\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[35.157419, "o", "  \u001b[1;32m✅ Gateway started on port 3000\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.158382, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m  Step 5: Verify security\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m  Testing unauthenticated request...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[38.165415, "o", "  HTTP 401 — \u001b[1;31mBlocked! Authentication required.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[41.166711, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m  Checking OAuth discovery metadata...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[42.185523, "o", "  {\r\n      \"resource\": \"http://localhost:3000/mcp\",\r\n      \"authorization_servers\": [\r\n          \"mcp-shield\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"mcp_protocol_version\": \"2025-06-18\",\r\n      \"resource_type\": \"mcp-server\",\r\n      \"bearer_methods_supported\": [\r\n          \"header\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"scopes_supported\": [\r\n          \"read:all\",\r\n          \"write:all\",\r\n          \"admin\"\r\n      ]\r\n  }\r\n"]
[46.212123, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;37m\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   ✅ MCP servers are now secured!                          ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   Features:                                               ║\r\n  ║   • JWT Authentication (strict mode)                      ║\r\n  ║   • Rate Limiting (token bucket, 60 req/min)              ║\r\n  ║   • CORS configured                                       ║\r\n  ║   • 3 servers federated → 1 secure endpoint               ║\r\n  ║   • OAuth 2.0 discovery metadata                          ║\r\n  ║   • Per-server endpoint isolation                          ║\r\n  ║   • Published to agentregistry                             ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   Built with:                                              ║\r\n  ║   • agentgateway (Linux Foundation)                        ║\r\n  ║   • agentregistry (Solo.io)                                ║\r\n  ║   • TypeScript + Commander.js                              ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n"]
[46.21228, "o", "  ║   npm install -g mcp-shield                                ║\r\n  ║   github.com/bcornish1797/mcp-shield                      ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n"]
[46.212428, "o", "  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n"]
